                    div(class='info col-12 col-lg-6')
                        h1(class='heading display-4 sen') Why You Need to Join Us
                        p(class='opensans text-dark lh-lg fw-regular my-4', style='--bs-text-opacity: .6;') Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt
